title: Oz Struggles to Woo Black Philadelphians in Senate Race
description: Dr. Mehmet Oz has been trying to reach Black voters in Pennsylvania’s most Democratic city as he runs for the Senate.
dc:creator: Trip Gabriel
media:credit: Hannah Beier for The New York Times
media:description: Dr. Mehmet Oz’s crime policy pitch in his race against John Fetterman includes supporting community policing, ending “sanctuary cities” and stopping fentanyl at the Southwest border.
